These are the best street tacos in Kansas City, hands down. Fresh made tortillas and pork carnitas prepared from large piece of rotisserie pork shaved off and then browned on the grill to add a little crispiness. Plenty of cilantro placed on the top and the price is unbeatable. Small restaurant is pretty much a hole in the wall, so little ambiance. But who cares, we pull up out front, grab our tacos and head out or occasionally eat in. Service is great and people are really nice. Don't miss out on the best street tacos in Kansas City. Finally, if you don't know what street tacos are, you're already missing out so get over there and have some. They are like American tacos only you don't need a bunch of cheese and sour cream on top for flavor. The meat has the flavor.
